&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience building or significantly contributing to a design system at a product company&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knows the foundations and the tool(s) for good visual design and UX&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of experience in design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Propensity to develop strong opinions, but hold them loosely&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A strong portfolio showcasing your design work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of no-code tools, like Framer or Weblow&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
